About Jaey

Where Style Meets Strategy

Jaey was founded by Jaini Haria, CA, MBA (XLRI), ex-Investment Banker, on one belief: that every woman deserves to dress with confidence, whatever her size, budget or background.

  • India's most loved power dressing brand for the professional woman
